OL,3,CWoman faces E34,000 medical bill after
OL,4,Cinsurance was invalidated because of
OL,5,CHRT
OL,7,FElle Dennis failed to declare she was
OL,8,Ftaking HRT when her travel policy
OL,9,Frenewed and must now pay thousands of
OL,10,Fpounds after needing unrelated medical
OL,11,Fcare, ITV News Correspondent Stacey
OL,12,FFoster reports
OL,14,FWords by ITV News Producer Catherine
OL,15,FDinneny.
OL,17,FA woman who needed urgent hospital
OL,18,Ftreatment while on holiday has been
OL,19,Frefused a pay out by her insurers
OL,20,Fbecause she failed to declare her
OL,21,Fmenopause medication.
