OL,3,CWoman faces E34,000 medical bill after
OL,4,Cinsurance was invalidated because of
OL,5,CHRT
OL,7,FElle Dennis had a seizure while on
OL,8,Fholiday in Majorca last year and
OL,9,Fneeded to be put into an induced coma,
OL,10,Fresulting in hospital stay costing
OL,11,FE34,000 (#28,000).
OL,13,FBut her claim has been denied by her
OL,14,Finsurer because she didn't mention
OL,15,Fthat she had been prescribed Hormone
OL,16,FReplacement Therapy when she renewed
OL,17,Fher policy - even though the
OL,18,Fmedication was unrelated to her fit.
