OL,5,CHRT
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News, she said: "I
OL,8,Ffeel really depressed and angry and
OL,9,Fworried. I don't know how I'm going to
OL,10,Fever pay the bill."
OL,12,FShe only started taking the medication
OL,13,Fat the end of April last year, just
OL,14,Fweeks before the couple went away with
OL,15,Ftheir children.
OL,17,FShe said: "I'd only just got the
OL,18,Ftablets, literally just before we went
OL,19,Fon holiday. I hadn't really taken
OL,20,Fthem."
