OL,7,FIt was the first day of their holiday
OL,8,Fwhen Elle was rushed to hospital after
OL,9,Fhaving a seizure. She was put in an
OL,10,Finduced coma and had to stay in a
OL,11,Fprivate clinic for seven days.
OL,13,FTests carried out while she was in
OL,14,Fhospital in Palma revealed she has a
OL,15,Fgrade three brain tumour.
OL,17,F"I actually asked that question (if it
OL,18,Fwas connected to HRT) and they said
OL,19,Fit's nothing to do with it at all,"
OL,20,FElle said.
