OL,5,CHRT
OL,7,FHer husband Neal added: "The doctors
OL,8,Fwere saying don't worry because you
OL,9,Fwill be covered under your insurance,
OL,10,Fthere's no way that you won't be
OL,11,Fcovered.
OL,13,F"We'd taken out medical insurance,
OL,14,Fwe'd taken our European health card.
OL,15,FShe was in a critical condition so the
OL,16,Fconcern was with trying to find out
OL,17,Fwhat exactly was going on."
OL,19,FNeal contacted Inter Parter
OL,20,FAssistance, part of the AXA group,
OL,21,Fwhile Elle was still in hospital.
