OL,7,FElle added: "Every woman goes through
OL,8,Fthe menopause. It's not a real medical
OL,9,Fcondition, it's just part of life, so
OL,10,Fit didn't even cross my mind (to
OL,11,Fdeclare it)."
OL,13,FElle and her husband Neal, who live in
OL,14,FRugeley in Staffordshire, are now
OL,15,Fbeing chased by debt collectors for
OL,16,Fthe money - all while Elle is
OL,17,Fundergoing gruelling cancer treatment
OL,18,Fback in the UK and unable to work.
