OL,7,FElle is now warning other women who
OL,8,Fare going through the menopause to
OL,9,Fcheck that they are covered when
OL,10,Ftravelling abroad.
OL,12,FShe said: "Declare everything, it's
OL,13,Fjust not worth it."
