OL,7,FRob Lilley-Jones, a consumer expert at
OL,8,FWhich?, said this case was unfair but
OL,9,Fadvised everyone to thoroughly check
OL,10,Ftheir policies because companies are
OL,11,Fincreasingly reluctant to pay out
OL,12,Fclaims.
OL,14,FHe said: "You wouldn't necessarily
OL,15,Fconsider going through the menopause
OL,16,Fto be a pre-existing medical
OL,17,Fcondition, but you do have to check
OL,18,Fthe terms and conditions of these
OL,19,Finsurance policies very, very
OL,20,Fcarefully.
