OL,7,FAn AXA Partners spokesperson told ITV
OL,8,FNews: "We sympathise with Mrs Dennis'
OL,9,Fsituation, however, she did not
OL,10,Fdeclare any previous medical
OL,11,Fconditions when renewing her annual
OL,12,Fmulti-trip travel insurance policy.
OL,14,F"It is crucial that any previous
OL,15,Fmedical conditions are declared when
OL,16,Fpurchasing a travel insurance policy.
OL,17,FIf she had declared, she may have been
OL,18,Foffered a different policy or we may
OL,19,Fnot have been able to provide her with
OL,20,Fcover.
